a servant, He opens the door of action and closes the door of disputation. If Allah wills harm for a servant, He closes the door of action and opens the door of disputation.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24327,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/01\/abu-sulaiman-ikhlaas-step\/","url_meta":{"origin":38124,"position":1},"title":"Abu Sulayman on Ikhlaas: Blessed are those who walk sincerely to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Qudamah reported: Abu Sulayman, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBlessed is he who takes a single step, desiring nothing but Allah Almighty.\u201d Ma\u2019ruf al-Karkhi would strike himself and say, \u201cO my soul! Be sincere and purify yourself!\u201d Source: Minha\u0304j al-Qa\u0304s\u0323di\u0304n 1\/365 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0642\u062f\u0627\u0645\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0633\u0644\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24323,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/01\/ibn-al-mubarak-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":38124,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Ikhlaas: Best deed is to be sincere to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Dunya reported: Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked, \u201cWhich deed is best?\u201d Ibn al-Mubarak said, \u201cSincerity to Allah.\u201d Source: al-Amr bil-Ma\u2019ru\u0304f li Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 71 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0646\u064a\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u00a0\u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064f\u0635\u0652\u062d\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 71 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0645\u0631 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0631\u0648\u0641\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35465,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/31\/maruf-ghurur\/","url_meta":{"origin":38124,"position":3},"title":"Ma\u2019ruf on Delusion: Foolish to rely on Allah\u2019s mercy while disobeying Him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Ma\u2019ruf al-Karkhi, may Alla have mercy on him, said, \u201cYour hope in the mercy of the One you refuse to obey is nothing but delusion and foolishness.\u201d Source: al-Muqliq li-Ibn al-Jawzi\u0304 1\/29 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0632\u064a \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0641 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0631\u062e\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0624\u064f\u0643\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0631\u06